5000|$|<b>The</b> <b>Mage's</b> Tale is a first-person dungeon crawler. Gameplay {{centers on}} {{exploring}} subterranean passages, solving puzzles, and fighting enemies. Unlike other games in The Bard's Tale series, <b>The</b> <b>Mage's</b> Tale {{focuses on a}} single character and class, a mage. Combat is real-time, using physical gestures to throw spells, and a magical shield to block incoming attacks.|$|R
