5000|$|<b>The</b> high <b>mages</b> in Armethalieh are the {{government}} and <b>the</b> law. Ambitious <b>mages</b> rise to <b>the</b> top of the social ladder through corruption and treachery, and {{the government}} is self-elected, maintaining a dictatorship over both mages and commoners. All goods and culture are censored, with many being rejected from the city as too new or different. <b>The</b> <b>mages</b> are obsessed with maintaining the pretence that all the work they do is [...] "for the good of the city".|$|R
